data.description: The seller will credit the buyer $5,000 at closing with an acceptance offer by 1-31-2024. Purchase this home today. This home comes with peace of mind with $10,000 of price protection included in the sale. REZITRADE Home price index protection. Need a Pool home for the New Year! This fantastic 4-bedroom, 3-bath property is a real "Must Have" for anyone looking for comfort and convenience all in one place. Get ready to experience the best of Florida living with your very own private pool, perfect for relaxing with family and friends. Inside, you'll find not one, but 2 master bedrooms, giving you that extra touch of luxury and flexibility. The kitchen and all three bathrooms are adorned with beautiful granite countertops, adding a touch of elegance to every corner. Plus, with ceiling fans in each room, you'll stay cool and comfy no matter the season. This home is incredibly versatile. Whether you're looking for a primary residence, a vacation getaway, or an excellent investment opportunity through short-term rentals like Airbnb or Vrbo, this property has got you covered. Located in the sought-after community of Calabay Parc, you will have easy access to all the amenities you need and the best local attractions, Don't miss out on this incredible chance to own a piece of paradise.  The updates to the master bathroom, such as new tile walls in the shower, have created a more luxurious and comfortable bathing experience. The installation of new granite countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms, along with a new backsplash in the kitchen, and stainless steel appliances have significantly elevated the overall look and feel of the home. A new hot water heater and air conditioning system in 2023, along with a new roof in 2021, The Newly modern pool pump is designed to circulate and filter the water in the pool, keeping it clean and well-maintained.  ensures that this home's essential systems are well-maintained and up to date. This home is fully up to date. Start living the life you've always dreamed of - come see this home today.  it won't last long.
